name.k: Tinybopによる無限のアーケード

platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 设计和玩自己的视频游戏！
ビデオゲーム組み立てキット
設計和玩自己的視頻遊戲！

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: We’ve played so many games that we feel like we could create our own—and now we can, all without coding classes or complex tutorials. With this ingenious educational app, it's easy to become a designer. Imagination rules as you build characters, worlds, and stories for one-of-a-kind games meant to be saved, shared, and—of course—played.
